MS text "Nobis prestatibus asta" - Correction taken from Bib. Braunschweig MS 86, f. 360v colophon. Abbey Saint-Benoit de Port-Valais, nr. 22709 (vol. 6, p. 421). Text layout has been altered slightly to make it performable, since, obviously, the text is not the original (e.g. the two parallel passages of the ouvert and clos have different numbers of syllables).
